divs: Sighting Detailsi was talking to 2 work mates after coming back from sydney,after sightings being reported over radio station over central coast that ufo,s were sighted,me sceptic having seen object s in my past, my self put it down to aircraft.well as i turned from talking to work mates to drive home behind my car as dusk set the siloweted trees in the back ground sudenly 6 bright round objects one larger than five others ,the largest sat in middle other 5 sat even distance around it they suddenly apeared headed toward tree line then done a perfect u turn with fenominal speed & acuracy as such they left traveling light behind them,but with no engine noise at all ,when i turned back to work mates and said did you see that they said what ,i went home and kept this to my self but i know what i seen with my eyes,it was truley awsome to see.
